title: MIJE Hostel
description: one of Three 'hotels for young people' in the heart of Paris. The MIJE (Maisons Internationales de la Jeunesse et des Etudiants)are a non profit-making organisation which manages three hotels for young people/students situated just a stone's throw from one another in the Marais quarter in the heart of Paris : Fauconnier, Maubuisson, Fourcy. All three are former aristocratic residences dating from the 17th century and have been renovated by the MIJE. 12 rue des Barres – 75004 Paris
